# What is SQL Developer?
SQL Developer is a software tool used in computing to work with databases. You can think of a database as a digital spreadsheet that stores important information, such as customer lists, inventory, or sales records. SQL Developer allows you to manage and retrieve this information more easily and efficiently.
## How to get SQL Developer?

You can download SQL Developer from the [**Oracle website**](https://www.oracle.com/tools/downloads/sqldev-downloads.html). You will need to create an account to download the software. Once you have downloaded the software, you can install it on your computer.